                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/3660: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Harbin</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hanson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Harbin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-10-03T18:00:00+08:26">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 3, 1924—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 8:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>General Manager Ostroumoff arrested and imprisoned by Chinese police; charges
                    unknown. Informed the Legation and Mukden.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hanson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
